snippet.title: More Pokémon Ultra Sun and Pokémon Ultra Moon Details Revealed!
snippet.description:
Get an early look at Pokémon Ultra Sun and Pokémon Ultra Moon, coming November 17! There are new buildings and landscapes in Alola—but that’s not all. Ominous dark clouds are spreading in the sky over Alola... What could this mean? Visit our site to learn more about these upcoming Pokémon games: http://bit.ly/2qT9MWT

US Preorders for Pokémon Ultra Sun: http://bit.ly/2v8cRnq
US Preorders for Pokémon Ultra Moon: http://bit.ly/2vJxPN7
